snippet: The American diving team that arrived in London this year represented a program that had not won a medal since 2000, but that changed last week.
abstract: American diving team had not won an Olympic medal since 2000, but that changed when United States teams won medals in three of the four synchronized events; as the individual events begin, success has spread a newfound confidence through the team.
lead_paragraph: The American diving team that arrived in London this year represented a program that had not won a medal since 2000, but that changed last week.

headline.seo: U.S. Diving Team Finally Tastes Olympic Success
headline.main: Less Practice Equals More Medals for U.S. Diving Team
headline.print_headline: Less Is More: Less Practice Equals More Medals
